"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640741368,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"PKGpdlEuiyQ2kgHvhPrMwX-bGyWILUeoV_2El6bQrog\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xfa2e53CfD4a46CE67d4D9f24598d4c199CA50B8A\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"X9UF5XWkTd4m0iZYYBMgVIWRvPJAjdXfKbB3_EFqNLE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q526mHT9H8VHu4KZ82N3DnHF6KS0Ph1Pw6JNPG07q94\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"b4O6uxVxzrf1bVUpAY87MA6g_jfiDchgNa9D-L4W_lPx588jjc7LIhVGim0_ccrD8lk2gKLdKuhSU6cy_rnHTg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3b3e4b47d3250ce08ffcba8fc9898b6e2c30e4cd27934db0990c6bb84bfef93739dce591aaa5b3981ca8c09d6171ef43ef3fb8e08b96129ccc1c80fb6bd071f91b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"X9UF5XWkTd4m0iZYYBMgVIWRvPJAjdXfKbB3_EFqNLE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q526mHT9H8VHu4KZ82N3DnHF6KS0Ph1Pw6JNPG07q94\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi